==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Gorm
<hw>Gorm</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>Axle grease. See
<er>Gome</er>.</def> <mark>[Prov. Eng.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Gorm</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Gorm
<hw>Gorm</hw>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <def>To daub, as the hands or clothing,
with gorm; to daub with anything sticky.</def> <mark>[Prov.
Eng.]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Gorma</ent>⟦br⟧
